---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - PT Global Niaga Sakti" description="Learn more about PT Global Niaga Sakti">
  <div class="min-h-[calc(100vh-396px)] bg-white py-6 sm:py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto">
        <!-- Top Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:gap-16 mb-12 lg:mb-16">
          <!-- Left Column -->
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
            <div class="rounded-[16px] overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
              <img 
                src="/src/assets/about/Harbour.png" 
                alt="Industrial Port" 
                class="w-full aspect-[16/10] object-cover"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-6">
              <h1 class="text-[32px] sm:text-[36px] md:text-[40px] lg:text-h1 font-bold text-primary-1 leading-tight">
                Empowering Industries<br />with Precision and<br />Innovation
              </h1>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <p class="text-base sm:text-body1 text-justify">
              <span class="font-semibold">PT Global Niaga Sakti</span> is your trusted partner in engineering, mechanical, electrical, and general services, supporting a wide range of industries, including manufacturing, automotive, consumer goods, chemicals, pharmaceuticals, marine, and more.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-body2 text-justify">
              With specialized expertise in sealing elements, we position ourselves as a reliable partner, providing not only high-quality products but also innovative solutions tailored to meet each customer's unique needs. Backed by a team of seasoned professionals, we ensure every solution is executed with precision and care.
            </p>

            <p class="text-base sm:text-body1 text-justify">
              Our commitment lies in delivering unmatched accuracy, responsiveness, and reliability, while fostering customer satisfaction, trust, and enduring partnerships.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
          <!-- Left Box -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-5">
            <div class="bg-primary-1 text-white rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 h-full">
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-body2 text-justify">
                PT Global Niaga Sakti is a company that consistently provides innovative solutions while maintaining a commitment to always prioritize quality, precision, and accuracy in all of its services. Always being a reliable partner that can be counted on by our customers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Center Box -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 flex items-center justify-center py-2 lg:py-0">
            <h3 class="text-[28px] sm:text-[32px] md:text-h3 font-bold text-primary-1 text-center">
              Vision<br />and<br />Mission
            </h3>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Box -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-5">
            <div class="bg-primary-1 text-white rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 h-full">
              <p class="text-sm sm:text-body2 text-justify">
                PT Global Niaga Sakti provides high-quality products and services that are always relied upon by customers both domestically and internationally. Supporting customer efficiency and productivity by offering comprehensive services aimed at long-term cooperation, while maintaining customer trust and satisfaction.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  img {
    image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .text-justify {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>